#To stop getting warnings:
import warnings
warnings.filterwarnings("ignore")
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np

#Here, to be able to apply to_datetime function, there was unclear entries in Time column
#All of them (38 items) have been deleted. These are the ones that I assigned big values while finding TimeStamp columns.
#I just deleted the items from .dat-Time-Added file.

data = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Data_Mining\\.dat-Time-Added.txt")

#When we check the types of the data frame, Value column's type is object.
#To groupby it, we need to convert it into numeric. But at first, we need to get rid off meaningless values
data["Value"]=data["Value"].replace(["0''","0Hi","3A","0Lo",np.nan],0)
data["Value"]=pd.to_numeric(data["Value"])


data=data.sort_values(["User ID", "Time_Stamp"],ascending = (True,True))
data.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Data_Mining\\Value-Replaced.txt", index=False )

count = 1
for i in range(1,71):
    dataseperate=data[data["User ID"].isin([i])]
    dataseperate["Index"]=dataseperate.index
    dataseperate.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(count) + ".txt", index=False )
    count=count+1
In [2]:
#Average of all Blood sugar levels up to that date.
#Before groupbying according to the date, there were some mistaken entries like 31-06.
#There is no 31st day in June. So, before starting, we converted it to 30 June by hand.

for i in range(1,71):
    average=0
    sum=0
    count=1
    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)-1):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        if (code== 48) | (code == 57)|(code== 58) | (code == 59)|(code== 60) | (code == 61)|(code== 62) | (code == 63)|(code== 64):
            sum=sum+value
            average=round(sum/count,2)
            liste.append(average)
            count=count+1
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste)-1])
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature1"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of all Blood sugar levels up to that date.
#Since 48 and 57 are related, they are removed.

for i in range(1,71):
    average=0
    sum=0
    count=1
    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)-1):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        if (code== 58) | (code == 59)|(code== 60) | (code == 61)|(code== 62) | (code == 63)|(code== 64):
            sum=sum+value
            average=round(sum/count,2)
            liste.append(average)
            count=count+1
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste)-1])
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature1_1"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of Unspecified Blood sugar levels up to that date.
for i in range(1,71):
    average=0
    sum=0
    count=1

    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)-1):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        if(code== 48) | (code == 57):
            sum=sum+value
            average=round(sum/count,2)
            liste.append(average)
            count=count+1
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste)-1])
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature2"]=seri
    print(datapatient[["Value","Feature2","Code"]].head(50))
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of all Blood sugar levels in the same category - pre
for i in range(1,71):
    average=0
    sum=0
    count=1

    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)-1):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        if(code== 58) | (code == 60)|(code== 62) | (code == 64):
            sum=sum+value
            average=sum/count
            liste.append(average)
            count=count+1
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste)-1])
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature3_Pre"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of all Blood sugar levels up to that date within the same time zone.

#Here, to be able to apply to_datetime function, there was unclear entries in Time column
#All of them (38 items) have been deleted. These are the ones that I assigned big values while finding TimeStamp columns.
#I just deleted the items from Value-Replaced file.
from datetime import datetime

tz1="00:00:00"
tz2="06:00:00"
tz3="12:00:00"
tz4="18:00:00"
tz5="23:59:59"

converted_tz1=datetime.strptime(tz1, '%H:%M:%S').time()
converted_tz2=datetime.strptime(tz2, '%H:%M:%S').time()
converted_tz3=datetime.strptime(tz3, '%H:%M:%S').time()
converted_tz4=datetime.strptime(tz4, '%H:%M:%S').time()
converted_tz5=datetime.strptime(tz5, '%H:%M:%S').time()
In [8]:
#Average of all Blood sugar levels up to that date within the same time zone. BedTime, Moning, Evening, Night
for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M").dt.time
    avrgb = 0
    avrgM = 0
    avrgE = 0
    avrgN = 0
    
    sumb = 0
    sumM=0
    sumN=0
    sumE=0
    countb = 1
    countM=1
    countE=1
    countN=1
    
    countere=1
    counterb=1
    counterm=1
    countern=1
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        if ((code == 48) | (code == 57) | (code == 58) | (code == 59) | (code == 60) | (code == 61) | (code == 62) | (code == 63) | (code == 64)):  # filtering according to codes
            
            if ((time>=converted_tz1) & (time<=converted_tz2)): #bedtime
                if counterb==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumb=sumb+value
                    avrgb=sumb
                    counterb=counterb+1
                    countb=countb+1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgb)
                    sumb=sumb+value
                    avrgb = sumb / countb
                    countb += 1
            elif ((time>=converted_tz2) & (time<=converted_tz3)): #morning
                
                if counterm==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumM = value
                    avrgM = sumM
                    counterm=counterm+1
                    countM +=1
                
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgM)
                    sumM=sumM + value
                    avrgM =sumM /countM
                    countM +=1
                
            elif ((time>=converted_tz3) & (time<=converted_tz4)): #Evening
                
                if countere==1:
                        liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                        sumE = value
                        avrgE = sumE
                        countere +=1
                        countE +=1
                else:
                        liste.append(avrgE)
                        sumE = sumE + value
                        avrgE = sumE /countE
                        countE +=1
                
            elif ((time>=converted_tz4) & (time<=converted_tz5)): #Night
                if countern==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumN = value
                    avrgN = sumN
                    countern += 1
                    countN +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgN)
                    sumN = sumN + value
                    avrgN = sumN / countN 
                    countN +=1
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
   # print(liste)
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature4_BMEN"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of all Blood sugar levels up to that date within the same time zone.Work Non Work
for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M:%S").dt.time
    avrgNon = 0
    avrgW = 0
    sumNon=0
    sumW=0
    countNon=1
    counterNon=1
    counterW = 1
    countW=1
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        if ((code == 48) | (code == 57) | (code == 58) | (code == 59) | (
                code == 60) | (code == 61) | (code == 62) | (
                code == 63) | (code == 64)):  # filtering according to codes
            
            if ((time>=converted_tz2) & (time<=converted_tz4)): #workhr
                
                if counterW==1: # To make up to date
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumW = value
                    avrgW= sumW
                    counterW += 1
                    countW +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgW)
                    sumW = sumW + value
                    avrgW = round( sumW / countW,2)
                    countW += 1
            elif ((time>=converted_tz1)  & (time<=converted_tz2)) | ((time >= converted_tz4) & (time<= converted_tz5)):
            
                if counterNon==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumNon = value
                    avrgNon = sumNon
                    countNon += 1
                    counterNon += 1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgNon)
                    sumNon = sumNon + value
                    avrgNon = round(sumNon / countNon,2)
                    countNon += 1
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
   # print(liste)
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature4_Work_NonWork"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of all Blood sugar levels in the same category up to that date within the same time zone. Pre Work-NonWork
for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M:%S").dt.time
    
    avrgb = 0
    avrgM = 0

    sumb = 0
    sumM=0
    
    countb = 1
    countM=1
    
    counterb=1
    counterm=1

    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        
        if ((code == 58) | (code == 60) | (code == 62) | (code == 64)):  # filtering according to codes
            
            if ((time>=converted_tz2) & (time<=converted_tz4)): #work
                if counterb==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumb = value
                    avrgb = sumb
                    counterb += 1
                    countb += 1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgb)
                    sumb = sumb + value
                    avrgb = sumb / countb
                    countb += 1
                    
            elif ((time>=converted_tz1)  & (time<=converted_tz2)) | ((time >= converted_tz4) & (time<= converted_tz5)):#nonwork
                if counterm==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumM = value
                    avrgM = sumM
                    counterm=counterm+1
                    countM +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgM)
                    sumM=sumM + value
                    avrgM =sumM /countM
                    countM +=1
            
                    
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
   # print(liste)
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature5Pre_WorkNonWork"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )
In [12]:
#Average of all Blood sugar levels in the same category up to that date within the same time zone. Post Morning Evening Bed Night
for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M:%S").dt.time
    
    avrgb = 0
    avrgM = 0
    avrgE = 0
    avrgN = 0
    sumb = 0
    sumM=0
    sumN=0
    sumE=0
    countb = 1
    countM=1
    countE=1
    countN=1
    
    countere=1
    counterb=1
    counterm=1
    countern=1
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        
        if ((code == 59) | (code == 61) | (code == 63)):  # filtering according to codes
            
            if ((time>=converted_tz1) & (time<=converted_tz2)): #bedtime
                if counterb==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumb = value
                    avrgb = sumb
                    counterb += 1
                    countb += 1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgb)
                    sumb = sumb + value
                    avrgb = sumb / countb
                    countb += 1
                    
            elif ((time>=converted_tz2) & (time<=converted_tz3)):#mor ning   
                
                if counterm==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumM = value
                    avrgM = sumM
                    counterm=counterm+1
                    countM +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgM)
                    sumM=sumM + value
                    avrgM =sumM /countM
                    countM +=1
            
            elif ((time>=converted_tz3) & (time<=converted_tz4)):#evening
                if countere==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumE = value
                    avrgE = sumE
                    countere +=1
                    countE +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgE)
                    sumE = sumE + value
                    avrgE = sumE /countE
                    countE +=1
            elif  ((time>=converted_tz4) & (time<=converted_tz5)): # night
                if countern==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumN = value
                    avrgN = sumN
                    countern += 1
                    countN +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgN)
                    sumN = sumN + value
                    avrgN = sumN / countN 
                    countN +=1
                    
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
   # print(liste)
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature5Post_BMEN"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

In [14]:
#Average of all Blood sugar levels in the same category up to that date within the same time zone. Unspecified Bed Morning Night Evening
for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M:%S").dt.time
    
    avrgb = 0
    avrgM = 0
    avrgE = 0
    avrgN = 0
    sumb = 0
    sumM=0
    sumN=0
    sumE=0
    countb = 1
    countM=1
    countE=1
    countN=1
    
    countere=1
    counterb=1
    counterm=1
    countern=1
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        
        if ((code == 48) | (code == 57)):  # filtering according to codes
            
            if ((time>=converted_tz1) & (time<=converted_tz2)): #bedtime
                if counterb==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumb = value
                    avrgb = sumb
                    counterb += 1
                    countb += 1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgb)
                    sumb = sumb + value
                    avrgb = sumb / countb
                    countb += 1
                    
            elif ((time>=converted_tz2) & (time<=converted_tz3)):#mor ning   
                
                if counterm==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumM = value
                    avrgM = sumM
                    counterm=counterm+1
                    countM +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgM)
                    sumM=sumM + value
                    avrgM =sumM /countM
                    countM +=1
            
            elif ((time>=converted_tz3) & (time<=converted_tz4)):#evening
                if countere==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumE = value
                    avrgE = sumE
                    countere +=1
                    countE +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgE)
                    sumE = sumE + value
                    avrgE = sumE /countE
                    countE +=1
            elif  ((time>=converted_tz4) & (time<=converted_tz5)): # night
                if countern==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumN = value
                    avrgN = sumN
                    countern += 1
                    countN +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgN)
                    sumN = sumN + value
                    avrgN = sumN / countN 
                    countN +=1
                    
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
   # print(liste)
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature5Unsp_BMEN"]=seri
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

    avrgb = 0
    avrgM = 0

    sumb = 0
    sumM=0
    
    countb = 1
    countM=1
    
    counterb=1
    counterm=1

    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        
        if ((code == 48) | (code == 57)):  # filtering according to codes
            
            if ((time>=converted_tz2) & (time<=converted_tz4)): #work
                if counterb==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
                    sumb = value
                    avrgb = sumb
                    counterb += 1
                    countb += 1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgb)
                    sumb = sumb + value
                    avrgb = sumb / countb
                    countb += 1
                    
            elif ((time>=converted_tz1)  & (time<=converted_tz2)) | ((time >= converted_tz4) & (time<= converted_tz5)):#nonwork
                if counterm==1:
                    liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])

#Average of all 00-06 Blood sugar levels up to that date.

for i in range(1,71):
    sum=0
    count=1
    avrg=0
    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M:%S").dt.time
    
    for j in range(len(datapatient)-1):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        
        if  ((code == 48) | (code == 57) | (code == 58) | (code == 59) | (code == 60) | (code == 61) | (code == 62) | (
                code == 63) | (code == 64)) & ((time>=converted_tz1) & (time<=converted_tz2)):
            sum = sum + value

            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
            

    seri=pd.Series(liste)

    count=1

    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M:%S").dt.time
    for j in range(len(datapatient)-1):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        if(((code== 66)|(code== 67)|(code== 68))&
        ((time>=converted_tz1) & (time<=converted_tz2))):

#Average of all Food intake levels in the same time zone BMEN

for i in range(1,71):
    avrgb = 0
    avrgM = 0
    avrgE = 0
    avrgN = 0
    sumb = 0
    sumM=0
    sumN=0
    sumE=0
    countb = 1
    countM=1
    countE=1
    countN=1
    countere=1
    counterb=1
    counterm=1
    countern=1

    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    #All "Time" column has been converted to Time format.
    datapatient['Time'] = pd.to_datetime(datapatient['Time'], format="%H:%M:%S").dt.time
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Value"]+1
        time=datapatient.loc[j,"Time"]
        if ((code == 66) | (code == 67) | (code == 68)):
            if ((time>=converted_tz1) & (time<=converted_tz2)): #bedtime
                if counterb==1:
                    liste.append(np.nan)
                    sumb = value
                    avrgb = sumb
                    counterb += 1
                    countb += 1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgb)
                    sumb = sumb + value
                    avrgb = sumb / countb
                    countb += 1
            elif ((time>=converted_tz2) & (time<=converted_tz3)):#mor ning 
                if counterm==1:
                    liste.append(np.nan)
                    sumM = value
                    avrgM = sumM
                    counterm += 1
                    countM +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgM)
                    sumM=sumM + value
                    avrgM =sumM /countM
                    countM +=1
            elif ((time>=converted_tz3) & (time<=converted_tz4)):#evening
                if countere==1:
                    liste.append(np.nan)
                    sumE = value
                    avrgE = sumE
                    countere +=1
                    countE +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgE)
                    sumE = sumE + value
                    avrgE = sumE /countE
                    countE +=1
            elif  ((time>=converted_tz4) & (time<=converted_tz5)): # night
                if countern==1:
                    sumN = value
                    avrgN = sumN
                    liste.append(np.nan)
                    countern += 1
                    countN +=1
                else:
                    liste.append(avrgN)
                    sumN = sumN + value
                    avrgN = sumN / countN 
                    countN +=1
        else:
            liste.append(np.nan)
   # print(liste)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature27_BMEN"]=seri
    datapatient["Feature27_BMEN"]=datapatient["Feature27_BMEN"].fillna(0)
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

In [39]:
#Converting timestamps to date and time

from datetime import datetime

def getdate(timestamp):
    ts = int(timestamp)
    return datetime.utcfromtimestamp(ts)
In [40]:
#Average of Food Intake in the last 4 hours.

for i in range(1,71):
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    datapatient.index=datapatient["Index"]
    del datapatient.index.name
    post_blood=[48,57,59,61,63]
    post_bloodfilter=datapatient["Code"].isin(post_blood)
    datafeature32 = datapatient[post_bloodfilter]
    dates = datafeature32['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)

    liste=[]
    
    for date in dates:
        # 4 hours = 240mins. Since the last time is not included, it becomes 241.
        dateRange =pd.date_range(end=date,freq='min',periods=241,closed="left") 
        xxx=datapatient[datapatient['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate).isin(dateRange)]
  
        liste.append(xxx[xxx["Code"].isin([66,67,68])].Value.mean())

    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    seri.index=datafeature32.index
    datapatient["Featuresız"]=seri

    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Featuresız"]
        if(code == 59)|(code == 61)|(code == 63)|(code == 48)|(code == 57):

            liste.append(value+1)
        else:
            liste.append(0)
 
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature29"]=seri
    datapatient["Feature29"]=datapatient["Feature29"].fillna(0)
    datapatient=datapatient.drop("Featuresız",axis=1)
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Time Elapsed since last meal (in hours, rounded down)
import numpy as np

for i in range(1,71):
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    datapatient.index=datapatient["Index"]
    del datapatient.index.name
    food=[66,67,68]
    foodfilter=datapatient["Code"].isin(food)
    datafeature37= datapatient[foodfilter]
    datafeature37["Time_Stamp1"]=datafeature37["Time_Stamp"].shift(1)
    fark=datafeature37["Time_Stamp"]-datafeature37["Time_Stamp1"]

    datapatient["Feature_35"]=round(fark/3600,0)
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Feature_35"]
        if(code== 66) | (code == 67)|(code==68):

            liste.append(value)
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste)-1])
 
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature35"]=seri
    datapatient=datapatient.drop("Feature_35",axis=1)
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

In [48]:
#Average of Regular Insulin Level in the last 6 hours.

for i in range(1,71):
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    datapatient.index=datapatient["Index"]
    del datapatient.index.name
    full_blood=[48,57,58,59,60,61,62,63,64]
    full_bloodfilter=datapatient["Code"].isin(full_blood)
    datafeature32 = datapatient[full_bloodfilter]
    dates = datafeature32['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)

    liste=[]

    for date in dates:
        # 6 hour = 360mins. Since the last time is not included, it becomes 361.
        dateRange =pd.date_range(end=date,freq='min',periods=361,closed="left") 
        xxx=datapatient[datapatient['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate).isin(dateRange)]
  
        liste.append(xxx[xxx["Code"].isin([33])].Value.mean())

    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    seri.index=datafeature32.index
    datapatient["Featuresız"]=seri

    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Featuresız"]
        if(((code == 48)|(code == 57)|(code == 58)|(code == 59)|(code == 60)|(code ==61)|(code == 62)|(code == 63)|(code == 64))& (np.isnan(value)==False)):

            liste.append(value)
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature37"]=seri
   # datapatient["Feature37"]=datapatient["Feature37"].fillna(0)
    datapatient=datapatient.drop("Featuresız",axis=1)
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

    full_bloodfilter=datapatient["Code"].isin(full_blood)
    datafeature32 = datapatient[full_bloodfilter]
    dates = datafeature32['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)

    liste=[]

    for date in dates:
        # 2 hours = 120mins. Since the last time is not included, it becomes 121.
        dateRange =pd.date_range(end=date,freq='min',periods=121,closed="left")

    datafeature32 = datapatient[full_bloodfilter]
    dates = datafeature32['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)

    liste=[]

    for date in dates:
        # 24 hours = 1440mins. Since the last time is not included, it becomes 1441.
        dateRange =pd.date_range(end=date,freq='min',periods=1441,closed="left") 
        xxx=datapatient[datapatient['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate).isin(dateRange)]
  
        liste.append(xxx[xxx["Code"].isin([69,70,71])].Value.count())

    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    seri.index=datafeature32.index
    datapatient["Featuresız"]=seri

    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Featuresız"]
        if (code== 48) | (code == 57)|(code== 58) | (code == 59)|(code== 60) | (code == 61)|(code== 62) | (code == 63)|(code== 64):

            liste.append(value)
        else:
            liste.append(0)
 
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature47"]=seri

    datapatient=datapatient.drop("Featuresız",axis=1)
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of all pre-supper Blood sugar levels up to that date in the same group 
#(check whether the value is pre- or post- food consumption and categorize accordingly)
#Pre
import pandas as pd
import numpy as np
for i in range(1,71):
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    datapatient.index=datapatient["Index"]
    del datapatient.index.name
    food=[66,67,68]
    foodfilter=datapatient["Code"].isin(food)
    datafeature54 = datapatient[foodfilter]

    dates = datafeature54['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)

    liste=[]
    for date in dates:
        # 8 hour = 480mins. Since the last time is not included, it becomes 481.
        dateRange =pd.date_range(end=date,freq='min',periods=481,closed="left") 
        liste.append(dateRange[0])

    seri=pd.Series(liste)

    presupper=[62]
    presupperfiltre=datapatient["Code"].isin(presupper)
    datafeature55=datapatient[presupperfiltre]

    datesdatafeature55 = datafeature55['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)
    datafeature55["Dates"]=datesdatafeature55
    filterfeature55=datafeature55["Dates"].isin(seri)
    datafeature55=datafeature55[filterfeature55]
    datapatient["Feature_53_Pre"]=np.cumsum(datafeature55["Value"]).shift(1)/np.arange(len(datafeature55))

    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False ) 
for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Feature_53_Pre"]
        if ((code== 62) & (np.isnan(value)==False))  :

            liste.append(value)
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature53_Pre"]=seri
    datapatient=datapatient.drop("Feature_53_Pre",axis=1)
    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )

#Average of all pre-supper Blood sugar levels up to that date in the same group 
#(check whether the value is pre- or post- food consumption and categorize accordingly)
#Post within 2 hrs

for i in range(1,71):
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    datapatient.index=datapatient["Index"]
    del datapatient.index.name
    food=[66,67,68]
    foodfilter=datapatient["Code"].isin(food)
    datafeature54_1 = datapatient[foodfilter]


    dates = datafeature54_1['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)

    liste=[]
    for date in dates:
        # 2 hour = 120mins. Since the last time is not included, it becomes 121.
        dateRange =pd.date_range(start=date,freq='min',periods=121, closed="right") 
        liste.append(dateRange)

    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    listefeature54=[]
    for j in seri:
        for k in j:
            listefeature54.append(k)

    presupper=[62]
    presupperfiltre=datapatient["Code"].isin(presupper)
    datafeature54_2=datapatient[presupperfiltre]

    datesdatafeature54_2 = datafeature54_2['Time_Stamp'].apply(getdate)
    datafeature54_2["Dates"]=(datesdatafeature54_2)

    filterfeature54_2=datafeature54_2["Dates"].isin(listefeature54)
    datafeature54_2=datafeature54_2[filterfeature54_2]
    datapatient["Feature_53_Post"]=np.cumsum(datafeature54_2["Value"]).shift(1)/np.arange(len(datafeature54_2))

    datapatient.to_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt", index=False )
for i in range(1,71):
    liste=[]
    liste.insert(0,np.nan)
    datapatient = pd.read_csv(r"C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\Yeni klasör\\"+ str(i) + ".txt")
    for j in range(len(datapatient)):
        code=datapatient.loc[j,"Code"]
        value=datapatient.loc[j,"Feature_53_Post"]
        if ((code== 62)  & (np.isnan(value)==False)) :

            liste.append(value)
        else:
            liste.append(liste[len(liste) - 1])
 
    liste.pop(0)
    seri=pd.Series(liste)
    datapatient["Feature53_Post"]=seri
    datapatient=datapatient.drop("Feature_53_Post",axis=1)

read_files = glob.glob('C:\\Users\\Lenovo\\Desktop\\eren\\*.txt')

    for f in read_files:
